---
title: Pork Meatloaf Parm over Spaghetti Marinara
description: Chicken Parm, Veal Parm, Meatball Parm… Pork Meatloaf Parm? Yes, dreams really do come true. Our chefs have Parm-ified individual pork meatloaves, layering them with mouthwatering marinara sauce and a cheesy panko topping. They’re baked until the meat is perfectly tender and the crust is crispy and melty, then served over spaghetti marinara with a sprinkle of more cheese for good measure. Parm-fection? We think so.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6203c357cfb77f04b013d9b0-2d90b2c3.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/pork-meatloaf-parm-6203c357cfb77f04b013d9b0-c81c61af.pdf
time required: 35 minutes
author: Michelle Doll Olson
servings: 2
nutrition:
  calories: 1070 kcal
  fat: 52 g
  saturated fat: 19 g
  carbohydrates: 98 g
  sugar: 18 g
  protein: 48 g
  fiber: 5 g
  sodium: 1580 mg
cuisine: Italian
course: main course
